channel.title: Out of Memory
channel.description:
I Receive this error when playing online, I play using the official client on http://www.runescape.com/game.ws?j=1, this is the output from the console:
[code]Error: n.TA qa.a:357 sk.a:704 la.a:1088 cb.d:135 cb.c:56 rh.a:103 fl.a:177 bn.a:197 mo.a:208 of.a:190 of.a:325 mn.a:35 sm.a:108 hd.a:43 client.h:2306 r.g:726 r.run:591 java.lang.Thread.run | java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: native(MPR) | [1)2760,5456,104,104|2)0,2813,5525|3)2|4)0|5)2|6)1423,690|7)false|8)0|9)false|10)false|11)false|12)true|13)102] [/code]
has anyone come across this error before?
i have tried setting max memory to 1024m yet the problem persists, i cant do anything without it crashing making pk or high risk (the fun bits) impossible to do...
